headline: Humana rises after favorable ruling peer UnitedHealth star rating
summary: Investing.com -- Shares of Humana Inc (NYSE:HUM) were up 2.5% at $305 after a favourable court ruling involving peer UnitedHealth Group (NYSE:UNH) over Medicare Advantage star ratings, boosting optimism about Humana's ongoing appeal regarding its own star scores.
